> Sprint Plan - A detailed plan outlining the specific tasks, goals, and timelines for a short-term 
                development cycle (sprint) within an agile framework like Scrum

> Here are some examples of actionable metrics:
Conversion rate
Retention rate
Churn rate
Number of active users (NAU)
Customer lifetime value (CLV)
Monthly recurring revenue (MRR)
Customer acquisition cost (CAC) 

Here are some examples of vanity metrics:
Trial users
Page views
Total number of users
Total customers acquired
Time on App
